                    reskilling. Belonging is achieved through virtual team connections, online collaboration tools like
                    Slack and Microsoft Teams, and digital team-building activities. Esteem needs are met through
                    recognition on digital platforms like GitHub's contribution graphs and Stack Overflow's reputation
