                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-running"></i> <strong>Expectancy:</strong> Effort → Performance belief
                            (GitHub contribution metrics)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-link"></i> <strong>Instrumentality:</strong> Performance → Reward linkage
                            (Stack Overflow reputation system)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-gift"></i> <strong>Valence:</strong> Value of rewards to individual
                            (personalized incentives)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> <strong>Digital tools:</strong> Performance tracking &
