                    </div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> <strong>Gibbs' Reflective Cycle:</strong> Description →
                            Feelings → Evaluation → Analysis → Conclusion → Action Plan</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i> <strong>Schön's Reflective Practice:</strong>
                            Reflection-in-action & Reflection-on-action</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> <strong>Digital applications:</strong> Feedback systems, 360
