                    behavior. Feelings can be captured through digital surveys and sentiment analysis tools. Evaluation
                    benefits from quantitative metrics available in digital environments like KPIs and performance
                    dashboards. Analysis can use data visualization tools to understand cause-effect relationships and
                    conduct root cause analysis. The conclusion phase can be enhanced with AI insights and expert
                    review. The action plan can be integrated with project management tools and OKR systems for
                    implementation and tracking.
